{"tid":1819247,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 4686名中國留學生被取消簽證　人數列首位且為5年來新高","createTime":"2020-01-10T15:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T15:48:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"674232cdb640b40fce8cb081ef0bb86c26e33b92","tid":1819247,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"澳洲內政部近日公布2018至2019年度的外國留學生數據，顯示去年度被澳洲取消簽證的中國留學生數目有4686人，為所有留學生中最多人失去簽證的群體。而去年度被取消簽證的中國留學生人數，更創下5年來的新高。<br />\n<br />\n去年度共有逾4萬5千名中國學生獲得澳洲學生簽證，最終有大批人失去簽證。據指，當中有很多人因上學時的出席率不足、提供虛假文件、或被查出<span style=\"color: red;\">利用學生身份到澳洲打黑工，而被政府取消簽證</span>。目前估計有逾6萬名黑工在澳洲，有4分之1為華人，其中有15%人是利用學生簽證入境。政府會對逾2個月沒有到校上課，但距離簽證到期日還有6個月以上的學生進行調查，以防有人濫用簽證。<br />\n<br />\n此外，也<span style=\"color: red;\">有留學生因犯罪、沒繳交學費或主動要求取消簽證等原因而失去簽證</span>。學校也會將留學生曠課及考試不合格等問題上報移民局。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200110/bkn-20200110200019703-0110_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200110%2Fbkn-20200110200019703-0110_00912_001.html&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjb%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=c7779b0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200110/bkn-20200110200019703-0110_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"42e5fc007b7146cbd81366240425242f08540982","tid":1819247,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefe2d507e668400635b2b2c1ab076f91dcca5af","tid":1819247,"uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"老貓又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513c8629e3a67e5f2f274e5